				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Thanks! I had equanimity and composure in mind when writing it; hadn&#8217;t put it together with buddhist vibes until you mentioned it, but it completely fits. <img src="http://localhost:8888/microfiction.co.za/wp-includes/images/smilies/simple-smile.png" alt=":)" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /></p>
